has been ranked as one of the premier hotels in Vietnam and a true heritage property within Southeast Asia. This was as true in 1960s, when the international press corps frequented the hotel for work, for accommodation and for entertainment, as it is in the economic boom years of the 2000s.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">After a major 1998 refurbishment, including construction of a complementary 24-storey tower, the hotel positioned itself at the forefront of Vietnam&rsquo;s hospitality scene. Now, the hotel is on the verge of its most significant makeover and refreshment &mdash; the perfect time to come onboard and start living our Mission, Vision, and Values &mdash; Guest First, Warmth, Respect, Harmony, Integrity and Kaizen.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">There are many doors into Caravelle Saigon, and opportunity knocks on all of them.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Please contact us via <a href=\"mailto:recruitment@caravellehotel.com\">recruitment@caravellehotel.com<\/a> and let us grow your future together.<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-4pkjv361 fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-12 fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"ffb-id-4pkk05sb fg-row row     fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"ffb-id-5chkd3q5 fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-4 fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"fg-vcenter-wrapper\"><div class=\"fg-vcenter\"><a class=\"ffb-id-5chkd3q7 responsive-image-wrapper fg-text-dark\" href=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/caravelle-hiring-generic-november-2022\" target=\"_blank\"><img decoding=\"async\"  srcset=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/caravellehiring-generic-Festive-2022.jpg 1339w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/638431abbdbf65de20724c36a038c80f_caravellehiring-generic-Festive-2022-320-c-100.jpg 320w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/638431abbdbf65de20724c36a038c80f_caravellehiring-generic-Festive-2022-768-c-100.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploa